{"tid":15490,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"尋找好食嘅南蠻炸雞便當","createTime":"2016-12-01T04:12:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T10:56:59.000Z","uid":28387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93444a1ad2bfedac0e20f13a7565b31f87ecf9fc","tid":15490,"uid":28387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/f3zptcxw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ff3zptcxw&h=af93058a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是咁的<br />\n當年重未u grad走左去尖沙咀個邊返part time<br />\n好記得the one地庫一樓<br />\n有間叫做東京便當嘅外賣店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知各位巴絲打有無食過<br />\n佢地個份南蠻炸雞便當簡直係世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟然d炸雞係一早炸定唔係即炸<br />\n但係店員會幫你加熱返<br />\n咪道依然<br />\n佢地嘅炸雞連埋比你嘅<br />\n他他醬同黑芝麻鹽飯一齊放入口<br />\n個種感覺就好似初戀<br />\n又好似中出完林早洩老母一樣<br />\n幾咁爽幾咁正<br />\n重點係成個便當四十幾蚊<br />\n又有野飲又有湯<br />\n同個呀姨講多飯多鹽多醬<br />\n佢又真係多比我<br />\n差唔多爆盒咁濟<br />\n<br />\n可惜嘅係<br />\n前個幾日想食返個飯<br />\n間野竟然已經執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n轉左第二間日式便當店<br />\n見到個間野同樣都有南蠻炸雞便當<br />\n唉<br />\n既然一場黎到咪試下好唔好食啦<br />\n買完個飯拎上手個時都覺得伏伏地<br />\n屌你老母林早洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又真係中撚左伏<br />\n成盒飯就好似食緊屎一樣<br />\n吳若希無KFC味<br />\n啲飯爛撚過屎<br />\n他他醬根本無他他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問下咁多位巴絲打<br />\n有無好食嘅南蠻炸雞便當推薦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afddb8ed97c5f8a2f8060df7c07b5ed139c1486c","tid":15490,"uid":35216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T04:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467d9160fde1f9a746dac95c92369822631100b4","tid":15490,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:57:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n九龍灣食堂個間執左"},{"pid":"de20532469ec7872bb8ec228baaae73b7281de6d","tid":15490,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:23:18.000Z","msg":"睇怕你要去日本先再食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4311ad13ea3dcb495499ecddb96ce792c607483","tid":15490,"uid":33694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:29:53.000Z","msg":"the one 下面果間好耐以前食過，真係好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&hellip;間嘢好似係吉之島的"},{"pid":"b9419bde907322822575fef8943ee2a6ea5c6fe1","tid":15490,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00343b42c666a66500391d05479cbb517190c5d7","tid":15490,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:31:33.000Z","msg":"南maan好好食&hellip;"},{"pid":"eab9cca11fb05a087bae2dde0c4b89d3bd8e2203","tid":15490,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:33:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>南maan好好食&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n未打完就send咗出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n南蠻炸雞真係好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc25dcf6feb4b9e9d7e54c0ee37137c6cc770db","tid":15490,"uid":2582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣Fire Bird, 幾好食, 價錢都ok"},{"pid":"ba78943e12cb44ce7aee9ce04d4fa2f4dcd5803e","tid":15490,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T10:44:55.000Z","msg":"垃圾炸雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72244a48d5a1973bcc7820a4b54bb7965be73c76","tid":15490,"uid":66679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T10:48:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28fb70808382f2dd626828875274c8f354f76dd7","tid":15490,"uid":5265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T10:50:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係呢個呀屌！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前坑口連里街都有一間 成日去食<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知香港邊度仲有呢間嘢 好想食返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔講都唔記得有依間野 以前成日食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cdc9481b4959f295d88f4d33f0891b55c8cce01","tid":15490,"uid":15206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T10:56:59.000Z","msg":"好鐘意食炸雞，下次試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}